text: Klyashevo (, ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Ukteyevsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 168 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Iglino, 14 km from Minzitarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Klyashevo, Iglinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
